&reftitle.description;
stringlibvirt_domain_snapshot_get_xml_desc resourcesnapshot
Provide an XML description of the domain snapshot.

&reftitle.parameters;





   snapshot



    The snapshot to dump. You can get snapshot resource using various functions(i.e. libvirt_list_domain_snapshots or libvirt_domain_snapshot_lookup_by_name) .
